  images: "images/download (2).jpg",
  text: "Movie Name : I Want to Eat Your Pancreas",
  desp: "I Want to Eat Your Pancreas is a Japanese coming-of-age anime film about a quiet high school boy who discovers that his cheerful classmate, Sakura Yamauchi, is suffering from a terminal pancreatic illness. As he keeps her secret, they form a deep emotional bond, exploring themes of love, mortality, and the value of living life fully."
},
{
  id: 1,
  images: "images/Suzume.jpg",
